<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Rubys 3D Prints</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Rubys 3D Prints helps turn ideas and print-ready files into real products through design support, prototyping, and custom 3D printing." />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #090c10;
      --bg-soft: #0d1218;
      --panel: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      --panel-2: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      --text: #ffffff;
      --muted: rgba(255,255,255,0.68);
      --muted-2: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
      --red: #ff4a43;
      --red-soft: #ff8b86;
      --red-pale: #ffd6d4;
      --shadow: 0 30px 120px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
      --radius: 28px;
      --radius-sm: 20px;
      --max: 1200px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

    .container {
      width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 48px));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .site-bg {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: -2;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 15% 10%, rgba(255,74,67,0.10), transparent 22%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 8%, rgba(255,255,255,0.06), transparent 18%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 40% 60%, rgba(255,74,67,0.06), transparent 24%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #090c10 0%, #0d1218 50%, #090c10 100%);
    }

    .site-grid {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: -1;
      opacity: 0.08;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 58px 58px;
      mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0.8), transparent 85%);
      -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0.8), transparent 85%);
    }

    .topbar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 18px;
      z-index: 40;
      padding-top: 18px;
    }

    .nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 24px;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .brand-logo {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      object-fit: contain;
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }

    .brand-title {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .brand-subtitle {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--muted-2);
      letter-spacing: 0.30em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 26px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover { color: white; }

    .hero {
      min-height: 100svh;
      display: grid;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 56px 0 96px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr;
      gap: 56px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,74,67,0.20);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      color: var(--red-soft);
      padding: 12px 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.28em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .eyebrow-dot {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--red);
      box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(255,74,67,0.6);
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 28px 0 0;
      font-size: clamp(52px, 8vw, 92px);
      line-height: 0.95;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .gradient-text {
      display: block;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ffffff 0%, #ffd6d4 50%, #ff8b86 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      color: transparent;
    }

    .lead {
      margin: 28px 0 0;
      max-width: 720px;
      font-size: clamp(18px, 2.2vw, 21px);
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 32px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 14px 26px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: transform .25s ease, background .25s ease, border-color .25s ease;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
    }

    .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .btn-primary { background: var(--red); color: white; }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: #ff5d57; }
    .btn-secondary {
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }

    .stats {
      margin-top: 42px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0,1fr));
      gap: 14px;
      max-width: 760px;
    }

    .card {
      position: relative;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--panel);
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      overflow: hidden;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }

    .card-pad { padding: 24px; }

    .stat-num,
    .section-eyebrow {
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.24em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,139,134,0.78);
    }

    .stat-text {
      margin-top: 12px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .hero-panel {
      position: relative;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border-radius: 34px;
      padding: 20px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      overflow: hidden;
      transform: translateY(var(--panel-offset, 0px));
      transition: transform .2s linear;
      will-change: transform;
    }

    .hero-panel::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(255,74,67,0.12), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at bottom left, rgba(255,255,255,0.06), transparent 30%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .panel-inner {
      position: relative;
      display: grid;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .workflow-box {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg,#121821,#0d1117);
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .workflow-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.24em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.42);
    }

    .workflow-list {
      margin-top: 26px;
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .workflow-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    }

    .workflow-num {
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .workflow-item.highlight .workflow-num {
      border-color: rgba(255,74,67,0.30);
      background: rgba(255,74,67,0.12);
      color: var(--red-pale);
    }

    .workflow-label { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.92); }
    .workflow-arrow { margin-left: auto; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.22); }

    .mini-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0,1fr));
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .mini-card {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 22px;
    }

    .mini-title {
      margin-top: 12px;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .mini-text,
    .body-text {
      margin-top: 12px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.62);
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    section.content-section {
      padding: 96px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .section-heading { max-width: 780px; }
    .section-title {
      margin: 18px 0 0;
      font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 56px);
      line-height: 1.08;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .cap-grid,
    .project-grid,
    .process-grid,
    .benefit-grid {
      margin-top: 56px;
      display: grid;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .cap-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0,1fr)); }

    .cap-card {
      padding: 28px;
      min-height: 260px;
      transition: transform .35s ease, border-color .35s ease, background .35s ease;
    }

    .cap-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      border-color: rgba(255,74,67,0.25);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.045);
    }

    .cap-plus {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: linear-gradient(145deg,rgba(255,74,67,0.18),rgba(255,255,255,0.08));
      color: var(--red-pale);
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .cap-title,
    .project-title,
    .process-title {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .project-header {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      align-items: end;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .text-link {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
      text-decoration: underline;
      text-underline-offset: 4px;
    }

    .project-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0,1fr)); }

    .project-card {
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: transform .35s ease;
    }

    .project-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); }

    .project-shell {
      position: relative;
      aspect-ratio: 16 / 11;
      padding: 24px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(255,74,67,0.18), transparent 26%),
        linear-gradient(135deg,#141a22,#0d1117 55%,#111722);
    }

    .project-inner {
      height: 100%;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 26px;
      padding: 24px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.03),rgba(255,255,255,0.01));
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    .project-top {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .project-num {
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.24em;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    }

    .project-tag {
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,74,67,0.20);
      background: rgba(255,74,67,0.10);
      color: rgba(255,214,212,0.85);
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .project-image {
      height: 160px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 22px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .project-image img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      transition: transform .6s ease;
    }

    .project-card:hover .project-image img { transform: scale(1.08); }

    .project-desc { margin-top: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); line-height: 1.8; font-size: 14px; }

    .process-layout {
      margin-top: 56px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .overview-card, .contact-card, .benefit-card { padding: 28px; }

    .overview-list { margin-top: 20px; display: grid; gap: 14px; }

    .overview-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      padding: 14px 16px;
    }

    .overview-num {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,74,67,0.25);
      background: rgba(255,74,67,0.10);
      color: var(--red-pale);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }

    .process-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0,1fr)); margin-top: 0; }
    .process-card { padding: 28px; }

    .benefit-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 0.95fr;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .benefit-stack { display: grid; gap: 12px; }
    .benefit-chip {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 16px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .contact-shell {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 34px;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 34px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(255,74,67,0.18), transparent 30%),
        linear-gradient(135deg,#121821,#090d11);
      box-shadow: 0 30px 120px rgba(0,0,0,0.40);
    }

    .contact-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 0.95fr;
      gap: 32px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .contact-title {
      font-size: clamp(38px, 5vw, 64px);
      line-height: 1.02;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      margin: 16px 0 0;
    }

    .contact-form {
      padding: 24px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    }

    .form-grid { display: grid; gap: 14px; }

    input, textarea {
      width: 100%;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      color: white;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      font: inherit;
      resize: vertical;
      outline: none;
    }

    input::placeholder, textarea::placeholder { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35); }
    textarea { min-height: 120px; }

    footer {
      padding: 30px 0;
      background: var(--bg);
    }

    .footer-grid {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .footer-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .footer-links a:hover { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); }

    .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(40px);
      transition: opacity .8s ease, transform .8s ease;
      will-change: transform, opacity;
    }

    .reveal.visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    .delay-1 { transition-delay: .08s; }
    .delay-2 { transition-delay: .16s; }
    .delay-3 { transition-delay: .24s; }
    .delay-4 { transition-delay: .32s; }

    @media (max-width: 1100px) {
      .hero-grid,
      .process-layout,
      .benefit-grid,
      .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .cap-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0,1fr)); }
    }

    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      .container { width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 28px)); }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .hero { padding-top: 34px; }
      .stats,
      .cap-grid,
      .project-grid,
      .process-grid,
      .mini-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .project-header { align-items: start; }
      .topbar { top: 10px; padding-top: 10px; }
      .nav { border-radius: 24px; }
      section.content-section { padding: 78px 0; }
      .contact-shell { padding: 22px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="site-bg"></div>
  <div class="site-grid"></div>

  <div class="topbar container">
    <nav class="nav reveal visible">
      <div class="brand">
        <img class="brand-logo" alt="Rubys 3D Prints logo" src="data:image/png;base64," />
        <div>
          <div class="brand-title">Rubys 3D</div>
          <div class="brand-subtitle">Prints</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="#capabilities">Capabilities</a>
        <a href="#work">Work</a>
        <a href="#process">Process</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </div>
    </nav>
  </div>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div class="reveal visible">
          <div class="eyebrow">
            <span class="eyebrow-dot"></span>
            Design • Prototype • Print
          </div>
          <h1>
            Build the
            <span class="gradient-text">idea first.</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="lead">
            rubys3dprints helps turn rough concepts into finished products through design support, rapid prototyping, and custom 3D printing. You can come with a file, sketch, screenshot, or just a problem to solve — or send an existing print-ready file and have it produced directly.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#contact">Start a Project</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#process">See the Process</a>
          </div>
          <div class="stats">
            <div class="card card-pad reveal visible delay-1">
              <div class="stat-num">01</div>
              <div class="stat-text">Idea-first workflow</div>
            </div>
            <div class="card card-pad reveal visible delay-2">
              <div class="stat-num">02</div>
              <div class="stat-text">File-ready printing available</div>
            </div>
            <div class="card card-pad reveal visible delay-3">
              <div class="stat-num">03</div>
              <div class="stat-text">Prototype to final part</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-panel" id="hero-panel">
          <div class="panel-inner">
            <div class="workflow-box reveal visible delay-1">
              <div class="workflow-header">
                <span>Workflow</span>
                <span>Idea to Product</span>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-list">
                <div class="workflow-item"><div class="workflow-num">01</div><div class="workflow-label">Idea</div><div class="workflow-arrow">→</div></div>
                <div class="workflow-item"><div class="workflow-num">02</div><div class="workflow-label">Design</div><div class="workflow-arrow">→</div></div>
                <div class="workflow-item highlight"><div class="workflow-num">03</div><div class="workflow-label">Prototype</div><div class="workflow-arrow">→</div></div>
                <div class="workflow-item"><div class="workflow-num">04</div><div class="workflow-label">Refine</div><div class="workflow-arrow">→</div></div>
                <div class="workflow-item"><div class="workflow-num">05</div><div class="workflow-label">Print</div><div class="workflow-arrow">→</div></div>
                <div class="workflow-item"><div class="workflow-num">06</div><div class="workflow-label">Deliver</div></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mini-grid">
              <div class="mini-card reveal delay-2">
                <div class="section-eyebrow">Best for</div>
                <div class="mini-title">Ideas that need direction</div>
                <div class="mini-text">Perfect for projects that are not fully designed yet and need help getting to a printable, usable part.</div>
              </div>
              <div class="mini-card reveal delay-3">
                <div class="section-eyebrow">Also available</div>
                <div class="mini-title">Direct file-to-print</div>
                <div class="mini-text">If you already have a finished file, you can skip the design stage and simply send it over for printing.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="capabilities" class="content-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-heading reveal">
          <div class="section-eyebrow">What We Do</div>
          <h2 class="section-title">A 3D printing company built around both design support and direct printing.</h2>
          <p class="lead" style="font-size:18px; max-width:820px;">The strongest part of your offer is flexibility. Some customers need help moving from idea to design to prototype, while others already have a finished file and simply need high-quality printing.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="cap-grid">
          <div class="card cap-card reveal"><div class="cap-plus">+</div><div class="cap-title">Concept Development</div><div class="body-text">Come with a rough idea, sketch, screenshot, or problem. We help shape it into something printable and useful.</div></div>
